{"tid":520792,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻腎病貓依兩日情況差咗","createTime":"2018-01-05T18:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T19:31:24.000Z","uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0176f743f3f2d29814ac5db16da04b2ed7ca119e","tid":520792,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T18:54:28.000Z","msg":"嘔多咗，極力反抗我餵食，食幾啖就嘔，再餵食完兩個鐘後又嘔返哂出尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n空肚到朝早都嘔水，已經好瘦，但真係餵唔到糧入佢個肚，以前超肥。<br />\n每次餵佢係強灌，佢好驚好唔開心哀嚎叫我唔好，我都好心痛，但唔通由得佢餓死咩。<br />\n佢而家好驚我行近佢，驚我捉佢食藥食糧，我都知可能要放手，十幾年感情真係好難放得開。<br />\n希望佢過兩日精神d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ccbcb983625846e62ef63ce17f0b7d4d82d417","tid":520792,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:04:20.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇同佢打水？"},{"pid":"b24cc346ca4ae73e6e55f8dbd492d7983fc24b31","tid":520792,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:05:08.000Z","msg":"打針啦"},{"pid":"4601a94c050b00f7e7441da6142c8ea70d67e6c7","tid":520792,"uid":115096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40ccbcb983625846e62ef63ce17f0b7d4d82d417","tid":520792,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:04:20.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇同佢打水？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"日日打水，佢唔吉針，剛剛又嘔完，晚餐加兩粒藥前工盡廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘔到冇力撻落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acc19310e784ba6d3a195df1971be713e162afe","tid":520792,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4601a94c050b00f7e7441da6142c8ea70d67e6c7","tid":520792,"uid":115096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40ccbcb983625846e62ef63ce17f0b7d4d82d417","tid":520792,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:04:20.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇同佢打水？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"日日打水，佢唔吉針，剛剛又嘔完，晚餐加兩粒藥前工盡廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘔到冇力撻落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"佢唔怕吉針"},{"pid":"de1417fb5774de36962fd3845640f47b200ebceb","tid":520792,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:22:15.000Z","msg":"今晚算啦，畀佢靜下。"},{"pid":"568bb70df6e0d8c6c9e26ec7191195e890fa2b8d","tid":520792,"uid":88449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1417fb5774de36962fd3845640f47b200ebceb","tid":520792,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:22:15.000Z","msg":"今晚算啦，畀佢靜下。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cccef6bde092efdf5fc5c51c8eb0cfc4fd1c954","tid":520792,"uid":88449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"完全明白你既感受，我之前主人都係咁"},{"pid":"f1e2f0d6dc575a2b9f6b7a033fb65e5476bd3e97","tid":520792,"uid":104383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T19:41:09.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明份報告幾差我都無放棄，但偏偏主子就好似一早看破生死咁。餵食，嘔，灌食，嘔。明明全日都呆到好似雕成咁，一打皮下水就發癲亂叫亂抓，一日比一日瘦。<br />\n<br />\n係打安樂針之前，真係好想有5秒可以比我地溝通到，5秒就夠，宜家一世遺憾"},{"pid":"eb31f799fa49ce81f0b774131d04f27d7496dc16","tid":520792,"uid":109050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"算啦,打針放過佢<br />\n腎病只會差唔會好"},{"pid":"09215fc65a80cc04b55dbd76a8a2a568658bb9ba","tid":520792,"uid":47681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T17:46:49.000Z","msg":"我都明白想救番佢<br />\n<br />\n我上次都係覺得隻貓有得救<br />\n之後姑娘話：佢肯食就到佢食 但如果情況壞到佢連吞都唔識吞你就要有心理準備<br />\n<br />\n最後都係冇辦法 我隻貓只撐到一日半就走左"},{"pid":"73ef541b45d68a43df9a5d8590bccfb5ed25c6d1","tid":520792,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T02:54:13.000Z","msg":"加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7b90cfb8fc92437de023e2285e2efad911f96e","tid":520792,"uid":115096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eb31f799fa49ce81f0b774131d04f27d7496dc16","tid":520792,"uid":109050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T15:39:34.000Z","msg":"算啦,打針放過佢<br />\n腎病只會差唔會好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T19:31:24.000Z","msg":"我明白腎衰竭冇得醫<br />\n只係拖時間<br />\n如果隻貓太辛苦我都會畀佢舒適咁離開<br />\n佢差咗幾日勁嘔之後穏定返叫得出聲<br />\n但身體比之前更差<br />\n朝早已經唔再行埋我腳邊叫我<br />\n全日冇哂精神縮埋發呆<br />\n食量減少三分一<br />\n再強灌都唔吞<br />\n之前只係半夜嘔水同早餐前嗅到貓糧味反胃即嘔<br />\n而家大約每5, 6個鐘就自己嘔淡黃色水 (今日4次)<br />\n不停流口水<br />\n我估佢都好唔開心又再消瘦<br />\n希望我唔會太令佢受折磨<br />\n唯一擔心佢拖到農曆年假期先毒發... 搵唔到醫生幫佢打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道要放手<br />\n但時間太難取決<br />\n我瞓啦"}]}